      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SPANGLEDSTAR (2) has held his form since winning four starts back, finishing 0.3L away two back and 0.7L off the winner most recently. She can sit closer this time around from an inside barrier and she has placed at this track and trip previously. Will be hard to hold out. FIREY PANZ (8) bounced back to form last start with a 1.2L off the winner most recently when a 40-1 pop. It's been a while between drinks, but she rates highly on the recent effort and has placed in 2/3 at this track and trip. Can go one better today without surprising. ALOTOFBANTER (4) has been narrowly beaten his past couple, missing out by a head last time at the 1200m trip here. Back to 1100m today won't be an issue and he can be prominent in the run. Expecting another bold performance. VIRESHA (3) will find this much easier than her resuming effort and can fire a shot for the new barn. DEEPLY ROOTED (1) has claims after closing strongly last time out.",
